ntrols to blend the ambience volume, offering options like \"Ninguno,\" \"Ruido Blanco,\" and \"Ruido Marr\303\263n Profundo.\" \"Viento C\303\263smico,\" a sine-modulated bandpass-filtered Brown Noise, sounds incredible. I\'m focusing on crafting an LFO for the frequency of a `BiquadFilterNode` to build \"Viento C\303\263smico.\" It\'s coming along amazingly.\n\n\n**Orchestrating the Sweep**\n\nI\'m now focusing on the 30-second frequency sweep. I\'m leveraging React\'s countdown with `setInterval` for the cycle\'s trigger. I\'ll implement a circular sequence of offsets for base carrier and binaural beat frequencies. I plan to use `setTargetAtTime` for smooth frequency transitions every 30 seconds, creating a comforting portamento sound.\n\n\n"
